name: South_Shore_Pure_Black_Axess_5-shelf_Bookcase
reviews: I bought this for our guest bedroom and it's a really nice addition to the room. Very sturdy and great finish.
Excellent product. Easy to put together.
great heavy duty quality a good value

these book shelves are pretty and good quality for the price. but as very heavy. So if you like to rearrange your living space often, this are a hassel to move. you may need a good set muscles around to help move them.
Two of us put together 2 of the units for our family room. It took some time and patience but the bookcases look nice with one on each side of a gray fireplace. They are very sturdy.

This is the 2nd purchase of this item. The first was the shorter 4 shelf. This was sufficient except it was damaged during rearranging of furniture in my room. I decided to order the taller more slender shelf. This fits even better in my nook space in my bedroom.
I just love my bookcases...and they go perfect in my home..thank you
My son is a big book lover and this bookshelf was a great way to display them in his room. Super easy to put together - good and solid, too. Can't beat the price!
